---
import PageLayout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import SeoMeta from '~/components/common/SeoMeta.astro';
---

<SeoMeta 
  title="SalesTag Use Cases — Real-World Applications"
  description="Discover how SalesTag transforms sales teams across industries. From door-to-door solar to high-end roofing, see real applications and success stories."
  url="https://salestag.io/use-cases"
  image="/assets/images/use-cases-og.png"
  schemaType="WebPage"
/>

<PageLayout>
  <main class="px-4 py-16 mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Built for the Frontlines</h1>
    
    <p class="text-xl mb-12 text-gray-600">
      SalesTag isn't just theory — it's deployed in high-stakes, face-to-face sales environments across industries. 
      Anywhere a human talks to another human to sell — we belong.
    </p>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Solar Sales</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        SalesTag was born on the roofs. We capture door-to-door solar consultations and in-home closes, 
        label critical sales moments, and feed that data back into AI-powered training loops.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Roofing & Restoration</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Insurance adjusters, damage inspectors, and sales reps operate in chaotic field conditions. 
        SalesTag creates structured data from messy phone calls and walkthroughs, helping close more claims.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Smart Home Alarms</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Fast-moving reps pitch high-emotion products like alarms and cameras. SalesTag flags pressure tactics, 
        optimizes rebuttals, and ensures legal compliance — all while coaching reps live.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Other High-Touch Verticals</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Car sales, pest control, door-knocking home services — if it's face-to-face and fast-moving, 
        SalesTag can listen, learn, and improve outcomes.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</PageLayout> 